    <module renderas="section" xml:id="openwebui-chat-input-field-usage">
      <merge>
        <title>The chat input field</title>
        <abstract>
          <para>
            For a new chat, the chat input field is located at the center of the
            &owui; chat window. During a chat session, the chat window slides to
            the bottom. Its main purpose is to accept a user prompt so that the
            AI can process it and respond (see
            <xref linkend="openwebui-chat-window-usage"/>). Besides that, the
            chat input field provides extended functionality that can help you
            achieve the following tasks.
          </para>
        </abstract>
      </merge>
