        <title>Setting the default AI model</title>
        <abstract>
          <para>
            In &owui;, you can specify an AI model in several contexts&mdash;for
            the current chat, for the current user or for the system default
            model. While the AI model set for the current chat overrides the
            user and system model, the user-specific model overrides the system
            model only.
          </para>
        </abstract>
